y $25\\%$. In addition, the resistive electromagnetic\nfields due to Ohmic-heating also play a non-ignorable role and must be included\nin real laser-solid interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2017 12:46:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-16"}
