idly increase with the scale. This feature is hidden\nin power spectrum analysis, which can undermine the usefulness of power spectra\nfor detailed studies of interstellar turbulence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2017 14:43:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Oct 2017 16:33:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 Oct 2017 15:27:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-29"}
